        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Understanding Mobile Surveillance Technology</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Learn how mobile surveillance trailers work and why they're the preferred security solution for temporary needs
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
