              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">3. Real-Time Alerts</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">When suspicious activity is detected, instant notifications are sent via app, email, or text message to designated personnel.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">4. Remote Intervention</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Two-way audio allows security personnel to warn off intruders in real-time, preventing incidents before they occur.</p>
